Protocol: Public Key Distribution

Types:
  Agent A, I, X;
  Number NA;
  Function pk;

Knowledge:
  A: A, I, X, pk(I);
  I: A, I, X, pk(I), inv(pk(I)), pk(X);

Actions:
  #---- (A authenticates to IdP and requests an authorization token) ----
  A -> I: {A, X, NA}pk(I)
  I -> A: {I, A, X, pk(X), NA}inv(pk(I))

Goals:
  A authenticates I on X, pk(X), NA